WEBVTT

00:06:59.875 --> 00:07:01.226
They would say things like,

00:07:01.250 --> 00:07:03.684
"Black people are the cursed
descendants of Ham,

00:07:03.708 --> 00:07:07.518
and they're cursed forever
into enslavement."

00:07:07.542 --> 00:07:09.643
This isn't, "I'm not racist."

00:07:09.667 --> 00:07:11.351
This is, "God's law."

00:07:11.375 --> 00:07:13.226
They would say things, like, you know,

00:07:13.250 --> 00:07:16.018
"Based on science, based on ethnology,

00:07:16.042 --> 00:07:18.184
based on natural history,

00:07:18.208 --> 00:07:20.518
black people by nature

00:07:20.542 --> 00:07:23.518
are predisposed to slavery and servility.

00:07:23.542 --> 00:07:26.393
This is nature's law. I'm not racist.

00:07:26.417 --> 00:07:30.226
I'm actually doing what nature
said I'm supposed to be doing."